### Unity
Unity does not have a built-in, explicit `Line` or `Polyline` class as part of its core GameObject primitives. Instead, it provides a `LineRenderer` component that can be attached to GameObjects. This component can render both simple and complex lines by setting a series of points in 3D space.

```csharp
